#: src/WebtreesApi.php:744
msgid ""
"Cannot create private/public keys, because the PHP extension openssl is not "
"available. Please install the PHP extension or create public/private keys "
"manually, e.g. by using OpenSSL on the command line."
msgstr ""
"Kan ikke oprette private/offentlige nøgler, da PHP-udvidelsen OpenSSL ikke "
"er tilgængelig. Installer PHP-udvidelsen, eller opret nøglerne manuelt, "
"f.eks. med OpenSSL fra kommandolinjen."

#: src/WebtreesApi.php:756
msgid "Failed to generate private/public keys"
msgstr "Oprettelse af private/offentlige nøgler mislykkedes"

#: src/WebtreesApi.php:757
msgid ""
"Please create public/private keys manually, e.g. by using OpenSSL on the "
"command line. Put the keys into the keys path, which is defined in the "
"module settings."
msgstr ""
"Opret venligst private/offentlige nøgler manuelt, f.eks. med OpenSSL fra "
"kommandolinjen. Placer nøglerne i den nøglesti, der er angivet i "
"modulindstillingerne."

#: src/WebtreesApi.php:758
msgid "Failed to write key to the following path"
msgstr "Kunne ikke oprette nøglen i mappen"

