#: resources/views/settings.phtml:80
msgid ""
"Currently, webtrees does not use the HTTPS protocol. It is highly "
"recommended to use HTTPS in order to ensure the encryption of access tokens "
"within API requests. HTTPS can be activated by changing \"base_url\" in the "
"\"config.ini.php\". Currently, \"base_url\" does not start with \"https://\"."
msgstr ""
"Webtrees kører i øjeblikket uden HTTPS. Det anbefales på det kraftigste at "
"aktivere HTTPS for at sikre, at access tokens krypteres i API-forespørgsler. "
"HTTPS aktiveres ved at ændre \"base_url\" i filen \"config.ini.php\". "
"\"base_url\" begynder i øjeblikket ikke med \"https://\"."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:90
msgid ""
"Currently, the path for the private/public keys is not a sub-directory of "
"the webtrees data folder. If the keys path lies within the webtrees "
"installation, it is highly recommended to use the webtrees data folder or a "
"sub-directory, because webtrees protects unauthorized access to this folder. "
"If you choose a folder outside of the webtrees data folder, the keys might "
"be unprotected against unauthorized access."
msgstr ""
"Stien til private/offentlige nøgler er i øjeblikket ikke en undermappe af "
"webtrees’ datamappe. Hvis nøglestien ligger i webtrees-installationen, "
"anbefales det kraftigt at bruge webtrees’ datamappe eller en undermappe "
"heraf, da webtrees beskytter denne mappe mod uautoriseret adgang. Hvis du "
"vælger en mappe uden for webtrees’ datamappe, kan nøglerne være ubeskyttede "
"mod uautoriseret adgang."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:95
msgid "Path for private/public keys"
msgstr "Sti til private/offentlige nøgler"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:101
msgid ""
"Path to the private/public keys. If a path is used within the webtrees "
"installation, it is highly recommended to use a path within the webtrees "
"data folder, because webtrees protects unauthorized access to the data "
"folder. The current settings (Control panel / Website preferences) for the "
"webtrees root and data folder are:"
msgstr ""
"Sti til private/offentlige nøgler. Hvis der anvendes en sti inden for "
"webtrees-installationen, anbefales det kraftigt at vælge en sti i webtrees’ "
"datamappe, da webtrees beskytter datamappen mod uautoriseret adgang. De "
"aktuelle indstillinger (Kontrolpanel / Webside indstillinger) for webtrees’ "
"rodmappe og datamappe er:"

